data.description:
Seller hates to let this one go, but has been relocated.  This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home sits on 6.95 acres with spring fed pond. Boasts metal barn with a tall lean-to for all your farm equipment. Sellers has crossed fenced a portion of pasture with a nice electric concreted wood post fence section. Home has a detached two car garage with 2 large storage closets in the back, in addition to that, it has a 3rd bay roll up door on the back side for more dry storage space.
Home has updated features, granite countertops, double ovens, two pantries, office nook and half bath in the mudroom.  Upon your arrival notice the nice long concrete drive up to the house.
